This interestingly works with SDK 3.0 and nnlib august 2017, but on both versions we have execution error -1.

body:
Thanks, @satok16. Could you provide insights on why the bellow error occurs while executing the graph standalone app on HVX? 

```
Using </data/keyboard_299x299.dat>
filesize=268203 elementsize=1 height=299 width=299 depth=3
Run!
execute got err: -1
hexagon/ops/src/op_output.c:59:output 0 too small
output size=4096
Rank,Softmax,index,string
0,0.000000,1023,OVERFLOW!
1,0.000000,1,kit fox
2,0.000000,2,English setter
3,0.000000,3,Siberian husky
4,0.000000,4,Australian terrier
run failed: -1
```
This interestingly works with `SDK 3.0` and `nnlib august 2017`, but on both versions we have execution error -1.
